# ============================
# .NET 8 and Blazor .gitignore
# ============================

# ** Visual Studio **
.vs/
# User-specific files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# ** Build Folders **
# Ignore build outputs in all src subdirectories
src/**/bin/
src/**/obj/
src/**/out/

# ** NuGet **
*.nupkg
# The packages folder can be ignored because of Package Restore
src/**/packages/*
# Except build/, which is used as an MSBuild target.
!src/**/packages/build/
# Uncomment if you have *.nuspec files
# src/**/*.nuspec

# ** ASP.NET Scaffolding **
src/**/ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

# ** StyleCop **
src/**/StyleCopReport.xml

# ** Rider **
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# ** Visual Studio Code **
.vscode/
.history/

# ** Logs and Databases **
*.log
*.sql
*.sqlite

# ** OS Generated Files **
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Icon?
Desktop.ini

# ** Publish Output **
src/**/publish/

# ** Backup & Report Files **
*_Backup_*
*_Report.xml

# ** Other Files to Ignore **
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.cache
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# ** Blazor Specific **
# No additional ignores required beyond standard .NET
# If you have client-side generated files that are not needed, add them here
